id.description:
The identifying string for this tag. This id must be unique per page to ensure properpage functions. If a generated id is provided, there is no reason to alter this property. This value canalso be used to reference this tag from other tags. For instance, the following is valid: 
"{
  "type": "text",
  "id": "myId"
}, {
  "type": "text",
  "value": "${myId.value}"
}
